{"tid":1860111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東累積逾700宗確診　取代浙江成為第二多個案省份","createTime":"2020-02-03T13:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T13:28:17.000Z","uid":21505,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67ebf8e11c55b0506d521022e84bc64f762f1307","tid":1860111,"uid":21505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情繼續擴散，內地確診個案突破一萬七千宗，361人死亡，已超過沙士在內地造成349人死亡的數字。<br />\n<br />\n內地至今有17302人確診染病，武漢所在的湖北省疫情仍然是最嚴重，超過11000人確診。廣東的個案突破700宗，已取代浙江成為第二多確診個案的省份。疫情已造成361人死亡，當中350人在湖北。<br />\n<br />\n港澳台確診個案目前合共33宗，全球其他地方的確診總數超過150宗，其中美國新增3宗確診個案，累積增至11宗。越南和印度亦有新增病例，分別累積有8宗和3宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=379172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379172&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d2b44dd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379172&h=bf4f1671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=379172</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下我地有政府唔驚既大媽依家驚唔驚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a150defb98e597c70730513b832cd21217844c8","tid":1860111,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22f7a9c26ca208c5ecf9a86a3d5a3d20341f339","tid":1860111,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"星塵回憶錄 - 香港(二) 612大戰　<br />\n<a href=\"https://l